Xingtai Weiyao Rubber and plastic products Co., Ltd. is located in North China adjacent to Shijiazhuang, Handan. Located in Pingxiang County, Xingtai City, Hebei Province. With many years of experience in manufacturing rubber products, plastic products, auto parts production, is a senior local enterprise, with a professional management team, marketing team and strong production capacity. At present, the company′s products are mainly operating and developing at home and abroad, exporting countries to the Middle East, America, Europe, Africa, Southeast Asia and other regions. As a part manufacturer, our purpose is to strengthen mutual understanding with customers and establish a partnership through good communication, so as to achieve win-win results.

The company to rubber products, plastic products, auto parts production. The main products include: Oil seal, valve stem oil seal, fan belt, V-belt, central bearing support, bushing, valve chamber cover, engine support, exhaust pipe pad, oil bottom shell pad, seat belt valve chamber cover, central support bearing and so on.

From the purchase of raw materials, the manufacture of parts, the final inspection of products and other procedures, the company has implemented a set of strict management system in accordance with the relevant international and domestic standards to ensure product quality. Over the years, we have won the recognition and trust of users with good service and products. The company′s products from design, production to sales are effectively run under the system, product quality has been strictly controlled. The company has a number of professional and technical personnel engaged in the industry for many years, integrating product surveying and mapping design, mold design and processing, compound formula design and mixing, process control and testing, to ensure the stability and reliability of product quality with more comprehensive technology and production advantages.

Xingtai weiyao rubber and plastic products Co., Ltd., located in xingtai, millennium ancient county, is an entity enterprise integrating r & D, production and sales. Our company specializes in the r & D and production of oil seal, o-ring, special-shaped rubber pad, plastic products, mechanical parts and other products. Our company accepts all kinds of customized products, and we have perfect production capacity for the development and production of special-shaped workpieces. The company has several independent brands: Hai na, borvke and airvsi. Adhering to the cooperation concept of quality first and customer first, our company has a number of fixed customers with long-term cooperation in Africa, southeast Asia, the Middle East, Europe and the United States.
